QuestData.Title: Lethtendris's Web
QuestData.Description: Blood Elf Lethtendris has web to catch magic here. She use for herself, but Master want to use for good of whole world! You help get web from stupid elf and not only will Dagg'thol reward you, you see how Master use it way better!
QuestData.RewardText: This web have lots of magic! Master will be very happy now!$B$BAnd you make Dagg'thol happy, $r. Take this so you believe how happy you make Dagg'thol!
